The uGFX Library can be found inside this repository at:
    bbb/meta-bbb/recipes-core/trebletrouble/files/src/ugfx/resources/ugfx/

The uGFX Library does not include its 3rd party components.

The uGFX Library is licensed under the GFX License, Version 1.2.
See COPYING.uGFX for further details.



fatfs can be found inside this repository at:
 bbb/meta-bbb/recipes-core/trebletrouble/files/src/ugfx/resources/ugfx/3rdparty/fatfs-0.10b/

 FatFs module is an open source software to implement FAT file system to
 small embedded systems. This is a free software and is opened for education,
 research and commercial developments under license policy of following trems.

  Copyright (C) 2014, ChaN, all right reserved.

 * The FatFs module is a free software and there is NO WARRANTY.
 * No restriction on use. You can use, modify and redistribute it for
   personal, non-profit or commercial product UNDER YOUR RESPONSIBILITY.
 * Redistributions of source code must retain the above copyright notice.


petitfs can be found inside this repository at:
 bbb/meta-bbb/recipes-core/trebletrouble/files/src/ugfx/resources/ugfx/3rdparty/petitfs-0.03/

 Petit FatFs module is an open source software to implement FAT file system to
 small embedded systems. This is a free software and is opened for education,
 research and commercial developments under license policy of following trems.

  Copyright (C) 2014, ChaN, all right reserved.

 * The Petit FatFs module is a free software and there is NO WARRANTY.
 * No restriction on use. You can use, modify and redistribute it for
   personal, non-profit or commercial use UNDER YOUR RESPONSIBILITY.
 * Redistributions of source code must retain the above copyright notice.


tinygl-0.4-ugfx can be found inside this repository at:
    bbb/meta-bbb/recipes-core/trebletrouble/files/src/ugfx/resources/ugfx/3rdparty/tinygl-0.4-ugfx/

uGFX support for TinyGL, 2014 Andrew Hannam

Some files have been modified to remove references to non-embedded
functions such as fprintf, exit and assert.

Copyright notice:

